data.message:
Official Top Notch Entertainment Announcement:
FAMILY, FRIENDS, RAPPERS, PRODUCERS, DJ's and any other talent you have associated with music, Kelvin and I will be hosting a contest/competition called "The Talent Over Fame Contest", presented by Top Notch Entertainment! The winner will receive 2 promotion videos on my youtube page, and a song of their choice on my next mixtape! This will be seen by all of my subscribers! First, to enter the contest you must subscribe to my youtube page (Boi35Baker) and second, send your entry in to ronron32285@gmail.com, saying that you subscribed and also with your song! You must have a youtube page to enter! After you send your entrees in, we will upload your entrees, as video to our page! It will be your job to promote the video and whoever gets the most likes on the video wins! We will decide the winner on November 31st, 2013! Have your beats and your bars ready because the competition starts now! Good luck! #TopNotchEntertainment #JetBlackEntertainment
